{"tid":1909370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有的手足不需要煩惱抗疫 因為他們永遠停留在2019","createTime":"2020-03-04T02:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T02:04:44.000Z","uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5983c1b421be5f6f2bdd7662d7a9df95511088","tid":1909370,"uid":140655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"這是2019年八月被香港黑警抓走時裙子走光的少女<br />\n她的自白 大意：<br />\n「那天的事是我多少晚的惡夢 曾經想過逃避 但是決定站出來對抗警暴<br />\n如果各位朋友 記者有當天的相片視頻證據 請聯繫天水連線<br />\n大家都在關注武漢肺炎 但是有的手足不需要煩惱抗疫 因為他們永遠停留在2019<br />\n我不會自殺 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wlkd6iuxizqbvm7/status/1234993946209599489?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwlkd6iuxizqbvm7%2Fstatus%2F1234993946209599489%3Fs%3D21&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=6bba16a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwlkd6iuxizqbvm7%2Fstatus%2F1234993946209599489%3Fs%3D21&h=054636d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wlkd6iuxizqbvm7/status/1234993946209599489?s=21</a>"}]}